name: Oxygone (Xvyce, orbitalrushem4, Winterprise, ULTIMATUM9000, Grios)
description:
Made from a 3-day game jam.

The world is in a nuclear disaster and oxygen is depleting out. Take care of the last remaining trees as much as you can to survive. 

WASD to move.
Space to interact.

GLHF!

  • Lead Programmer- ULTIMATUM9000
